{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467090/extras/IntroText.jpg?t=1738112456\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467090/extras/GIF.gif?t=1738112456\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467090/extras/PitchText.png?t=1738112456\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We are in the year 2452 on the planet CECLON, in galaxy 732.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Z-One team has been sent there to recover the Veka energy that abounds on the planet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This energy can be used to power all sorts of things, and above all to create water and artificial food. With the earth's resources in short supply, man sees this energy as a future solution for the survival of the human race.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Subsequently, a second expedition, the Z-Two team, was sent to the planet to assist the Z-One team in their task.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But during their journey, Z-One team gave no sign of life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Soon arriving at their destination, the Z-Two team unfortunately collided with an asteroid shower on the outskirts of the planet, which caused major damage to the Nexentia shuttle. Too badly damaged, it crashed on a plateau, leaving no survivors... Except Jensen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Alone in this arid desert, you must survive, understand what happened and leave the planet CECLON, bringing the precious Veka energy back to Earth. Will you fail in your mission, or will you be a survivor and savior of humanity?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467090/extras/CharacteristicsText.png?t=1738112456\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Made by a lone developper, THE DARK SIDE OF CECLON is a TPS open-world with unique blend of action/adventure with survival/RPG mechanics. An immersive game set in a science fiction universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467090/extras/Characteristics.png?t=1738112456\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1467090/extras/EndText.png?t=1738112456\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Survival is essential","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467090/d72c4dbe5debd27ccc766038a6da405a9be97309.jpg"},{"name":"It's just a boost","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467090/e34723acb830e75f5b9d83ccf7c06810d083dc8d.jpg"},{"name":"Never tired","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467090/078a25d5fa2e1e60d88692aaf612c25cc4d793ea.jpg"},{"name":"Plunderer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467090/54a98bbfa6cc19025cd01864250b74e8f43f1880.jpg"},{"name":"Great sleeper","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467090/3981e06d515ab5600b173fab887e5a300ec9efb7.jpg"},{"name":"Endless Desert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467090/51f8bc2757ae19625c28e890ef1ee6e475435ba7.jpg"},{"name":"A real maze","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467090/6a90da5676282282fe1fd96f577ba15bb6dc19a6.jpg"},{"name":"Controller","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1467090/d616d93ace8a9f856e2070d6c2f8eecf028fdd1f.jpg"},{"name":"Great Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/14670